metadata.name: The Translucent #1
metadata.description:
EDITION 1 OF 1

Collection: The Translucent Paintings  
Artist: Godwits  
Year: 2022

The Translucent Collection by Godwits is a tribute to Mother Earth. This collection of 100 unique 1/1 works harmoniously blend the five elements on a digital canvas.

In a world where everything is digital, The artist wanted the viewers to take a deep breath, relax and dedicate a moment of the viewers time to remember the beauty and importance of the five elements that Mother Nature gifted our people.

The elements of life: Earth, Fire, Water, Air, and Metal.

Published By: Abstract Art Labs LLC  
Smart Contract Type: Manifold / ERC-721  
Artist Royalty: 10%
